responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "F28C1D3F448F013CC3DCEAB1BF0795CC", "Not a chance, sapling. You do good work, but your technique is lacking. Get some time out in the woods and focus on soft wood like Oaks. Get your technique in order, and you\'ll be an apprentice in no time.")
